{"tid":1069743,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[請人]我哋做咗個教外國人廣東話嘅網，想搵有熱誠嘅你同我哋一齊努力","createTime":"2019-03-20T07:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:30:34.000Z","uid":223799,"like":134,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1f014634f86b3a3b897ace03de841b2df62866d2","tid":1069743,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"Our website: <a href=\"https://www.howtostudycantonese.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtostudycantonese.com%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=8df9fae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.howtostudycantonese.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我哋係一個免費教人講廣東話網站。我哋嘅對象係喺香港嘅外國人，同埋喺海外嘅香港人後代，希望幫佢哋學到去native嘅級數。經過咗幾個月嘅發展之後，我哋唔單止改善咗個網站嘅UI，我哋亦都組織咗一條專業嘅team，並喺2月做咗商業登記。我哋會喺今年中開始發展啲賺得多啲嘅產品。我哋條team依家有product designer、電台嘅報導員、同我自己做網頁設計同教廣東話文法。我哋知道連登臥虎藏龍，而我哋條team又全部都係經連登識嘅，所以想喺呢度試吓公開請人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋之前嗰兩個post:<br />\n我哋做咗個教外國人廣東話嘅網<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/914547/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/914547/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋做咗個教外國人廣東話嘅網（二）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1021227/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1021227/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋都有太大諗頭，畀人屌到飛起嘅時候：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/937919/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/937919/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n依家我哋準備擴展我哋嘅business，之後會做一系列專業嘅廣東話podcast同簡單介紹廣東話詞語嘅article，希望搵到適合嘅人可以同我哋一齊合作。<br />\n<br />\n我哋介紹廣東話詞語嘅article例子：<a href=\"https://www.howtostudycantonese.com/category/cantonese-vocabulary%EF%BC%88%E8%A9%9E%E5%BD%99%EF%BC%89/how-do-you-say-this-in-cantonese/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtostudycantonese.com%2Fcategory%2Fcantonese-vocabulary%25EF%25BC%2588%25E8%25A9%259E%25E5%25BD%2599%25EF%25BC%2589%2Fhow-do-you-say-this-in-cantonese%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=fd3e4643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.howtostudycantonese.com/category/cantonese-vocabulary%EF%BC%88%E8%A9%9E%E5%BD%99%EF%BC%89/how-do-you-say-this-in-cantonese/</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋想搵呢一類人：<br />\n<br />\n要求（廣東話podcast）：<br />\n-對推廣廣東話有熱誠<br />\n-有廣播經驗<br />\n-最好對粵拼有基本認識，可以分到懶音<br />\n<br />\n工作內容：<br />\n-寫podcast要用嘅稿<br />\n-參與錄音<br />\n<br />\n要求（廣東話詞語嘅article）：<br />\n-對推廣廣東話有熱誠<br />\n-肯自己睇書，進修廣東話文法<br />\n-最好對粵拼有基本認識<br />\n<br />\n工作內容：<br />\n-寫article<br />\n<br />\n酬勞：你做嘅作品賺到嘅LikeCoin 100%歸你<br />\n喺呢度睇吓咩係LikeCoin: <a href=\"https://like.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flike.co%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=be65abc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://like.co/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你係我哋搵緊嘅人，即刻tg我哋啦: <a href=\"https://t.me/howtostudycantoese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhowtostudycantoese&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=cbc6cbf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/howtostudycantoese</a><br />\n如果你唔符合上述嘅條件，又想用自己嘅專長幫手嘅，都好歡迎你留個tg 講畀我哋知你有咩專長。我哋會睇吓之後有冇機會搵你幫手。"},{"pid":"cd100c130454133adee609cda4d18f640fa297db","tid":1069743,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"100924fb919ff6139d230d1961ff3ac442c2c06c","tid":1069743,"uid":112459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"part-time 得唔得"},{"pid":"93f2d4b0368dcc1310c05161657ca685aff28735","tid":1069743,"uid":199139,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"點解要識粵拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb59f80ab8337950e3ec89cf0dc906970e50f4f","tid":1069743,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"100924fb919ff6139d230d1961ff3ac442c2c06c","tid":1069743,"uid":112459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"part-time 得唔得